body: I ended gold 5 last season, I didnt get rewarded the border or maokai skin????? so confused

replies.body: Rewards for season 6 have been distributed. Reach out to us in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) if you haven't received yours and we can offer more context.   We'll get back to you!
